xt-align: center\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Years\n|-\n|align=left|Ezequiel Simone\n|align=left|1914\n|-\n|align=left|Leonardo Pareto\n|align=left|1915\n|-\n|align=left| Augo Vaccaro\n|align=left|1915\n|-\n|align=left|Ludovico Bacchiani\n|align=left|1916\n|-\n|align=left|Guido Farti\n|align=left|1917\n|-\n|align=left|Dulio Frugoli\n|align=left|1918\n|-\n|align=left|Valentino Sola\n|align=left|1918\n|-\n|align=left|Menotti Falchi\n|align=left|1919\u20131920\n|-\n|align=left|David Pichetti\n|align=left|1921\u20131922\n|-\n|align=left|Francisco De Vivo\n|align=left|1923\u20131924\n|-\n|align=left|Giuseppe Perrone\n|align=left|1925\u20131927\n|-\n|align=left|Eduardo Matarazzo\n|align=left|1928\u20131931\n|}\n|width=\"30\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Years\n|-\n|align=left|Dante Delmanto\n|align=left|1932\u20131934\n|-\n|align=left|Raphael Parisi\n|align=left|1934\u20131938\n|-\n|align=left|\u00cdtalo Adami\n|align=left|1939\u20131940\n|-\n|align=left|Enrico de Martino\n|align=left|1939\u20131940\n|-\n|align=left|Jo\u00e3o Minervino\n|align=left|1939\u20131940\n|-\n|align=left|\u00cdtalo Adami\n|align=left|1941\u20131944\n|-\n|align=left|Francisco Patti\n|align=left|1945\u20131946\n|-\n|align=left|Higino Pellegrini\n|align=left|1947\u20131948\n|-\n|align=left|Ferr\u00facio Sandoli\n|align=left|1949\u20131950\n|-\n|align=left|M\u00e1rio Frugiuelle\n|align=left|1951\u20131952\n|-\n|align=left|Pascoal Walter Byron Giuliano\n|align=left|1953\u20131954\n|-\n|align=left|M\u00e1rio Beni\n|align=left|1955\u20131958\n|-\n|align=left|Delfino Facchina\n|align=left|1959\u20131970\n|-\n|align=left|Paschoal Walter Byron Giuliano\n|align=left|1971\u20131976\n|}\n|width=\"30\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Years\n|-\n|align=left|Jord\u00e3o Bruno Sacomani\n|align=left|1977\u20131978\n|-\n|align=left|Br\u00edcio Pompeu Toledo\n|align=left|1977\u20131978\n|-\n|align=left|Delfino Facchina\n|align=left|1979\u20131980\n|-\n|align=left|Br\u00edcio Pompeu Toledo\n|align=left|1981\u20131982\n|-\n|align=left|Paschoal Walter Byron Giuliano\n|align=left|1983\u20131984\n|-\n|align=left|N\u00e9lson Tadini Duque\n|align=left|1985\u20131988\n|-\n|align=left|Carlos Bernardo Facchina Nunes\n|align=left|1989\u20131992\n|-\n|align=left|Mustaf\u00e1 Contursi Goffar Majzoub\n|align=left|1993\u20132005\n|-\n|align=left|Afonso Della Monica Netto\n|align=left|2005\u20132009\n|-\n|align=left|Luiz Gonzaga de Mello Belluzzo\n|align=left|2009\u20132011\n|-\n|align=left|Arnaldo Tirone\n|align=left|2011\u20132012\n|-\n|align=left|[[Paulo Nobre]]<ref>[http://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/palmeiras/noticia/2013/01/paulo-nobre-derrota-perin-e-e-o-novo-presidente-do-palmeiras.html]. ''Globo Esporte'', article \"Eleito presidente do Palmeiras, Nobre afirma: 'N\u00e3o sou salvador da p\u00e1tria'\". Accessed on January 21, 2013.</ref>\n|align=left|2013\u20132016\n|-\n|align=left|Mauricio Galiotte<ref>[http://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/palmeiras/noticia/2016/11/candidato-unico-mauricio-galiotte-e-eleito-para-presidencia-do-palmeiras.html]. ''Globo Esporte'', article \"Novo presidente, Galiotte quer que Cuca continue no Palmeiras em 2017'\". Accessed on November 26, 2016.</ref>\n|align=left|2016\u2013\n|}\n|}\n\n==Records==\n\n===Top scorers===\n[[File:Heitor.jpg|thumb|200px|Heitor]]\nThese are Palmeiras's top scorers since its foundation (data as of 1 February 2016):\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:left;\"\n|-\n! #\n! Name\n! Goals\n! Years\n|-\n|1\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ettore Marcelino Dominguez|Heitor]]\n|327\n|1916\u201331\n|-\n|2\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[C\u00e9sar Augusto da Silva Lemos|C\u00e9sar Maluco]]\n|180\n|1967\u201374\n|-\n|3\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Ademir da Guia]]\n|153\n|1961\u201377\n|-\n|4\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} Lima\n|149\n|1938\u201354\n|-\n|5\n|{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Serv\u00edlio de Jesus Filho|Serv\u00edlio]]\n|140\n|1963\u201368\n|