=\n\nCrefisa, a Brazilian bank, announced it would sponsor Palmeiras for the 2015 season.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://esportes.terra.com.br/sao-paulo/novo-chapeu-palmeiras-supera-sao-paulo-e-fecha-com-crefisa,f75a5f138021b410VgnVCM20000099cceb0aRCRD.html|title=Novo chap\u00e9u? Palmeiras supera S\u00e3o Paulo e fecha com Crefisa|work=Terra|accessdate=January 22, 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150124163214/http://esportes.terra.com.br/sao-paulo/novo-chapeu-palmeiras-supera-sao-paulo-e-fecha-com-crefisa,f75a5f138021b410VgnVCM20000099cceb0aRCRD.html|archive-date=January 24, 2015|url-status=dead|df=mdy-all}}</ref> After their success in the [[2016 Campeonato Brasileiro S\u00e9rie A|2016 Campeonato Brasileiro]], Crefisa announced it would increase fundings to R$90 million.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://torcedores.com/noticias/2017/01/crefisa-patrocinio-palmeiras-investir|title=CREFISA DEVE AUMENTAR PATROC\u00cdNIO E PALMEIRAS PODE GANHAR FOR\u00c7A PARA INVESTIR|work=Torcedores|accessdate=January 3, 2017}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n!Period\n![[Kit (association football)|Kit]] manufacturer\n!Shirt partner\n|-\n|1977\u20131986\n|rowspan=3| [[Adidas]]\n||<small>''None''</small>\n|-\n|1987\u20131988\n|| [[Agip]]\n|-\n|1989\u20131992\n|| [[Coca-Cola]]\n|-\n|1993\u20131995\n|| Rhummell\n|rowspan=3| [[Parmalat]]\n|-\n|1996\u20131999\n|| [[Reebok]]\n|-\n|1999\u20132000\n|rowspan=2| Rhummell\n|-\n|2001\u20132002\n|rowspan=3| [[Pirelli]]\n|-\n|2002\u20132005\n|| [[Diadora]]\n|-\n|2006\u20132007\n|rowspan=7| [[Adidas]]\n|-\n|2008\n|| [[FIAT]]\n|-\n|2009\u20132010\n|| [[Samsung]]\n|-\n|2010\u20132012\n|| [[FIAT]]\n|-\n|2012\u20132013\n|| [[Kia Motors|KIA]]\n|-\n|2013\u20132014\n|| <small>''None''</small>\n|-\n|2015\u20132018\n|rowspan=2|Crefisa<ref>{{cite web|title=Presidente da Crefisa comemora sucesso da parceria|url=http://www.verdao.net/noticia.php?n=14677|accessdate=17 July 2015|language=Portuguese}}</ref>\n|-\n|2019\u2013prese