ne}}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=  |p=Dentist |s=Vitor Ugo Salvoni}}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=  |p=Massagists |s=Serginho<br />Alan<br />Paulinho}}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=  |p=Nurse|s=Daniel Lima}}\n{{Fb cs staff |bg=  |p=Podiatrist|s=Edson Silva}}\n{{Fb cs footer|u=08 January 2020 |s=[http://www.palmeiras.com.br/futebol/comissao Palmeiras]|date=May 2015}}\n<!--\nTemplate:Fb cs staff (Football - coach staff - staff)\n\nParameters\nbg : background color. y = yes; blank = no\np  : staff position\ns  : staff\n\nTemplate:Fb cs footer (Football - coach staff - footer)\n\nParameters\nu  : date of last update\ns  : source\n-->\n\n===Presidents===\nThe club associates congregate in a general assembly every four years to elect the seventy-six members of the Conselho Deliberativo (''Deliberating Council'')<ref>''Estatuto da Sociedade Esportiva Palmeiras'' (club statute), art. 52.</ref> who in their turn chose amongst them a president for a two-year mandate.<ref>''Estatuto da Sociedade Esportiva Palmeiras'' (club statute), art. 83.</ref> As of 2006 the president can only be re-elected once.<ref>''Estatuto da Sociedade Esportiva Palmeiras'' (club statute), art. 113.</ref>\n\nThese are all Palmeiras presidents since the club's foundation:<ref>Sociedade Esportiva Palmeiras official records and meeting minutes</ref><ref>[http://paginas.terra.com.br/esporte/palmeirasminhavida/index_arquivos/Page1342.htm]{{dead link|date=December 2017|bot=InternetArchiveBot|fix-attempted=yes}}. ''Terra'', Chapter \"Palmeiras Minha Vida\", article \"Presidentes do Palmeiras\". Accessed on December 24, 2007.</ref>\n\n{|\n|-\n|width=\"30\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center\"\n|-\n! Name\n! Years\n|-\n|align=left|Ezequiel Simone\n|align=left|1914\n|-\n|align=left|Leonardo Pareto\n|align=left|1915\n|-\n|align=left| Augo Vaccaro\n|align=left|1915\n|-\n|align=left|Ludovico Bacchiani\n|align=left|1916\n|-\n|align=left|Guido Farti\n|align=left|1917\n|-\n|align=left|Dulio Frugoli\n|align